sumnerpoems00sumnrich_0287_22:0.0250:* Colonel Chapin, of the One Hundred and Sixteenth New York,
sumnerpoems00sumnrich_0287_23:0.0000:Commander of our brigade ; and, as is hinted, an inveterate drill-
